headline: Spotting Winners: Reynolds (NASDAQ:REYN) And Household Products Stocks In Q4
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at household products stocks, starting with Reynolds (NASDAQ:REYN).
